quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,Ta Sin Mim
  26,2,Awa ndi mawu omveka a Buku la Korani
  26,3,Iwe mwina ukhoza kudziononga ndi madandaulo chifukwa cha kusakhulupirira kwawo
  26,4,"Ngati Ife tifuna, tikhoza kuwavumbulutsira chizindikiro chochokera kumwamba chimene makosi awo adzakhota modzichepetsa"
  26,5,Palibe chenjezo latsopano limene limadza kuchokera kwa Mwini chisoni chosatha koma iwo amalikana
  26,6,Ndithudi iwo amakana mawu a Mulungu koma nkhani zidzadza kwa iwo zokhudza zinthu zimene iwo amazichita chipongwe
  26,7,"Kodi iwo saona nthaka, mmene ife tameretsamo mbewu zabwino zosiyanasiyana"
  26,8,Ndithudi m’menemu muli chizindikiro komabe ambiri a iwo sakhulupirira ayi
  26,9,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndiponso Mwini chisoni chosatha